# wayland-protocols is intentionally unversioned: meson.build wants >= 1.47,
# which Debian 13 / Ubuntu 24.04 do not ship yet. When the system copy is too
# old, meson falls back to subprojects/wayland-protocols.wrap (downloaded at
# configure time — hence ca-certificates).
